<body class="one-page" style="min-width:100%;">
<!--~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ Font ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~-->	
<link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:300' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
<div class="preloader white"><span class="loader"><span class="loader-inner"></span></span></div>

<div class="main">
  <section
	class="section call-action-section"
	data-background-image="/assets/backgrounds/starlake.jpg"
	data-shadow="rgba(0,0,0,0.02)"
	data-nav-color="rgba(255,255,255,0.4)"
	data-nav-color-text="rgba(0,0,0,1)"
	data-color="#768088"
	data-title-color="#ffffff"
	data-title="Home"
	data-anchor="home">
	<div class="section-content">
	  <div class="section-wrap" >
		<div class="container" >
		  <div class="row" >
			<div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12 info text-center">
			  <h1 class="section-title font-selector" data-appear-animation="bounceInUp" data-appear-animation-delay="100"><strong>Welcome, <%= @user.first_name %>!</strong><br>You have discovered Ratafire</h1>
			  <a href="#why" class="btn btn-lg btn-info font-selector" data-appear-animation="bounceInUp" data-appear-animation-delay="300">Start Tutorial</a>
			</div><!-- .info -->
		  </div>
		</div>
	  </div>
	</div><!-- .section-content -->
  </section><!-- .section -->

  <section
	class="section call-action-section"
	data-background-color="#cccccc"
	data-shadow="rgba(0,0,0,0.02)"
	data-nav-color="rgba(0,0,0,1)"
	data-nav-color-text="#01957d"
	data-color="#666666"
	data-title-color="#666666"
	data-title="why"
	data-anchor="why">
	<div class="section-content not-scroll">
	  <div class="container section-wrap">
		<div class="row promo-box inverse text-center">
		  <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
			<div class="features-text" data-appear-animation="fadeInDown" data-appear-animation-delay="600">
			  <h1 class="section-title font-selector">Why We Created Ratafire?</h1>
			  <p class="descriptions color-grey">We believe that artists and researchers should work on what they love and be properly supported by those who understand their talent.</p>
			</div><!-- .features-text -->
			
			<img src="/assets/macbook.png"
				 data-big="/assets/macbook@2x.png"
				 class="zoom-img replace-2x"
				 width="750"
				 height="447"
				 alt=""
				 data-appear-animation="bounceInUpBig">
		  </div>
		</div><!-- .promo-box -->
	  </div>
	</div><!-- .section-content -->
  </section><!-- .section -->
  
  <section
	class="section align-without-title services-section"
	data-background-image="/assets/backgrounds/sky.jpg"
	data-shadow="rgba(0,0,0,0.03)"
	data-nav-color="rgba(255,255,255,0.4)"
	data-nav-color-text="rgba(0,0,0,1)"
	data-title-color="#ffffff"
	data-title="subscription"
	data-anchor="subscription">
	<div class="section-content ">
	  <div class="container section-wrap">
		<h1 class="section-title text-center font-selector" data-appear-animation="fadeInDown" data-appear-animation-delay="900">Start Receiving Monthly Subscription</h1>
		  
		<div class="services-wrap inverse no-appear">
		  <div class="wrap-container">
			<div class="column column-one">
			  <div class="circle-wrap" data-appear-animation="zoomIn" data-appear-animation-delay="600">
				<canvas class="circle-skill" data-color="#f2f2f2" data-percent="75" data-title="A Discussion" width="150" height="150"></canvas>
				<div class="description">
				  <h3 class="title">Lead a Discussion</h3>
				  <div class="text">
					<p>You then must start at least one discussion thread and curate it. Monthly subscription on Ratafire isn't only about your personal projects.</p>
					<p>The discussions you participated count towards your contribution to this community. Read our <a><i class="fa fa-comments-o"></i> Community Guidelines </a> to learn more.</p>			
				  </div>
				</div>
			  </div>
			</div><!-- .column-one -->
			
			<div class="column column-two">
			  <div class="circle-wrap" data-appear-animation="zoomIn" data-appear-animation-delay="400">
				<canvas class="circle-skill" data-color="#f2f2f2" data-percent="60" data-title="A Project" width="150" height="150"></canvas>
				<div class="description">
				  <h3 class="title">An On-going Project</h3>
				  <div class="text font-selector">
					<p>You must create at least one on-going project and make the project digitally available. You can also collaborate with others on the same project.</p>
					<p>You should update your projects frequently, and improve their quality relentlessly. Visit our <a href="https://www.facebook.com/ratafire" target="_blank" ><i class="fa fa-facebook-square"></i> Facebook Page</a> for our weekly featured projects.</p>
				  </div>
				</div>
			  </div>
			  
			  <div class="circle-wrap" data-appear-animation="zoomIn" data-appear-animation-delay="500">
				<canvas class="circle-skill" data-color="#f2f2f2" data-percent="65" data-title="Application" width="150" height="150"></canvas>
				<div class="description">
				  <h3 class="title">Apply to Turn on Subscription</h3>
				  <div class="text">
					<p>You can then apply to turn on subscription. We will review your application and inform you of the result within 1 business day.</p>
					<p>To apply, you will need to write your "To Subscribers" page and connect your account to Amazon Payments.</p>					
				  </div>
				</div>
			  </div>
			</div><!-- .column-two -->
			
			<div class="column column-three column-center">
			  <div class="circle-wrap main-circle" data-appear-animation="zoomIn" data-appear-animation-delay="100">
				<div class="circle-content">
				  <h3 class="title color-grey">Click on each requirement to reveal its details</h3>
				</div>
				
				<div class="opened-content">
				  <a href="#" class="close">
					<svg version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" viewBox="0 0 24 24" enable-background="new 0 0 24 24" xml:space="preserve">
					  <path fill="inherit" d="M23.3,23.3c-0.6,0.6-1.5,0.6-2.1,0L0.7,2.8c-0.6-0.6-0.6-1.5,0-2.1c0.6-0.6,1.5-0.6,2.1,0
					  l20.5,20.5C23.9,21.8,23.9,22.7,23.3,23.3L23.3,23.3z M23.3,2.8L2.8,23.3c-0.6,0.6-1.5,0.6-2.1,0c-0.6-0.6-0.6-1.5,0-2.1L21.2,0.7
					  c0.6-0.6,1.5-0.6,2.1,0C23.9,1.3,23.9,2.2,23.3,2.8L23.3,2.8z"/>
					</svg>
				  </a>
				</div><!-- .opened-content -->
			  </div><!-- .main-circle -->
			</div><!-- .column-three -->
			
			<div class="column column-four">
			  <div class="circle-wrap" data-appear-animation="zoomIn" data-appear-animation-delay="700">
				<canvas class="circle-skill" data-color="#f2f2f2" data-percent="90" data-title="All or Nothing" width="150" height="150"></canvas>
				<div class="description">
				  <h3 class="title">All or Nothing</h3>
				  <div class="text">
					<p>If you sucessfully complete the 10 supporters in 30 days challenge, you can now start to receive monthly subscription fees via Ratafire.</p>
					<p>You can also keep your first 10 supporters/subscribers should you succeed. However, if you fail, you will lose them. You can always apply again.</p>					
				  </div>
				</div>
			  </div>
			  
			  <div class="circle-wrap" data-appear-animation="zoomIn" data-appear-animation-delay="800">
				<canvas class="circle-skill" data-color="#f2f2f2" data-percent="60" data-title="10 Supporters" width="150" height="150"></canvas>
				<div class="description">
				  <h3 class="title">Find first 10 Supporters in 30 Days</h3>
				  <div class="text">
					<p>Once your application is approved, before you can receive monthly subscription fees normally, you must find the 10 supporters/subscribers in 30 days.</p>
					<p>Tell your friends about your profile on Ratafire. Invite them to join your discussions, and they may become one of your subscribers!</p>					
				  </div>
				</div>
			  </div>
			</div><!-- .column-four -->
			
			<div class="column column-five">
			  <div class="circle-wrap" data-appear-animation="zoomIn" data-appear-animation-delay="900">
				<canvas class="circle-skill" data-color="#f2f2f2" data-percent="80" data-title="In 30 Days" width="150" height="150"></canvas>
				<div class="description">
				  <h3 class="title">In 30 Days</h3>
				  <div class="text">
					<p>You must find your first 10 supporters/subscribers in 30 days. We believe that this time constraint can help you focus on finding subscribers and improving your projects.</p>
					<p>You can find a countdown timer on your subscribers page. Others can also see your progress in this challenge.</p>					
				  </div>
				</div>
			  </div>
			</div><!-- .column-five -->
		  </div><!-- .wrap-container -->
		</div><!-- .services-wrap -->
	  </div>
	</div><!-- .section-content -->
  </section><!-- .section -->
  
